  m_Name: 4 stasius
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  planet: 4
  descriptions:
  - 'Stasius is similar to Earth in that it is a relatively new planet in the Championship. '
  - 'Stasians are quite similar to humans in their appearance, apart from their skin
    being green and being much more muscular due to the stronger gravity of their
    planet. This means that their biology allows them to wield the bow and arrow
    quite well. '
  - 'Unlike Earth, they have never throughout their history invented archery so this
    discipline is quite new for them. During the last intergalactic championship,
    they won all of their games against 4 planets and have earned the possibility
    of a second player. '
  - This is the first time they will have 2 players representing them. Stasius is
    often called the pink planet as a large proportion of the planet is covered by
    the hoko plant, a pink plant which grows across the planet.
